Not that I don't see the overall point of your post, dans, because I actually DO agree (my primary alternate is a 56 Chanter), but even though bards wear plate, our incoming damage mitigation isn't much better than other classes wearing silk.  If what I'm saying is an exageration, it's not one by very much.
<br />

<br />
I didn't really mean that as a nit-pick of your post, just more really as a soap-box opportunity for re-stating that our incoming damage mitigation is horrible already (especially when you consider we are a PLATE class).  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" />
<br />

